48:16.163 --> 48:18.263
MARK:
<i>"Nicol,</i>

48:18.265 --> 48:21.233
<i>without the 'E' on the end,"</i>

48:21.235 --> 48:23.203
she says.

48:25.740 --> 48:27.472
To be continued.

48:27.474 --> 48:30.310
(SIGHS) That's sweet.

48:32.547 --> 48:36.049
Mm, that's one heck of a story.

48:37.752 --> 48:40.087
It's kind of violent.

48:41.523 --> 48:44.289
But at least
the Nazis are dead.

48:44.291 --> 48:46.726
- That's good.
- Well, for a while.

48:46.728 --> 48:50.162
They seem to have
more than one life.

48:50.164 --> 48:52.230
And I like that Nicol.

48:52.232 --> 48:54.168
She's pretty clever.

48:56.136 --> 48:58.172
I like her, too.

