49:51.091 --> 49:53.026
♪

50:04.271 --> 50:06.273
I do love dames.

50:17.752 --> 50:20.586
Sweet dreams, Nicol.

50:20.588 --> 50:22.322
Welcome.

50:27.160 --> 50:29.162
