Good night, girls.

50:31.566 --> 50:33.499
MARK:
<i>I think they're in love.</i>

50:33.501 --> 50:36.368
What does Deja have to say
about all this?

50:36.370 --> 50:38.270
Ugh. She's not happy.

50:38.272 --> 50:42.173
Last night, I actually
caught her trying to...

50:42.175 --> 50:45.176
- What?
- Nothing.

50:45.178 --> 50:47.379
I mean, I know that you
were saying that I'm crazy,

50:47.381 --> 50:48.881
but I just personally don't
trust this Belgian Witch.

50:48.883 --> 50:50.716
I think you need
to keep an eye on her.

50:50.718 --> 50:52.317
