Nicol, without the "E."

51:00.327 --> 51:02.862
CARLALA: Right.
And who is she named after?

51:02.864 --> 51:05.665
- No one in particular.
- You're not gonna tell me?

51:05.667 --> 51:08.166
Hey, Mark.
You got a phone call.

51:08.168 --> 51:10.335
