from work?

51:54.247 --> 51:55.681
Yeah.

51:55.683 --> 51:57.550
Can I ask you a favor?

51:57.552 --> 52:01.721
Um, I have a hutch inside
that I need help moving.

52:01.723 --> 52:04.790
Would you mind
giving me a hand?

52:04.792 --> 52:06.892
- Sure.
- Okay.

52:06.894 --> 52:13.733
♪ I only have eyes

52:13.735 --> 52:16.602
♪ For you

52:16.604 --> 52:19.239
Uh, okay. Okay.

52:25.813 --> 52:30.816
♪ I don't know if

52:30.818 --> 52:36.691
♪ We're in a garden...

52:38.559 --> 52:40.225
Thank you.

52:40.227 --> 52:42.427
It's really heavy.
(CHUCKLES)

52:42.429 --> 52:44.429
How's your day?
Are you having a good day?

52:44.431 --> 52:46.464
- Good. Yeah.
- Yeah?

52:46.466 --> 52:49.369
- I like that hat.
- Thank you.

52:50.738 --> 52:53.639
- Welcome.
- Thank you.

