53:35.348 --> 53:36.851
(DOOR CLOSES)

53:52.533 --> 53:54.969
What the hell?

53:56.070 --> 53:57.837
(NICOL GRUNTS)

53:57.839 --> 54:00.573
My brother is into stilettos.

54:00.575 --> 54:03.408
Six-inch heels or higher.

54:03.410 --> 54:06.411
