live up in New Haven.

54:06.413 --> 54:09.014
- MARK: Mm-hmm.
- He...

54:09.016 --> 54:11.751
He also collects lingerie.

54:11.753 --> 54:14.287
- MARK: Mm.
- (NICOL PANTING)

54:16.924 --> 54:19.024
NICOL:
Hmm.

54:19.026 --> 54:21.560
I just collect shoes.

54:21.562 --> 54:23.796
You have a shoe collection?

54:23.798 --> 54:26.899
I have 287 pairs.

54:26.901 --> 54:30.368
Oh, so you only have
a shoe fetish?

54:30.370 --> 54:31.937
Oh, I wouldn't
call it a fetish.

54:31.939 --> 54:34.774
I'd call it essence.

54:34.776 --> 54:36.709
A woman's essence.

54:36.711 --> 54:39.979
I collect women's essence.

54:39.981 --> 54:44.784
When I wear them...
I don't know why...

54:44.786 --> 54:49.354
they somehow connect me
to the essence of dames.

54:49.356 --> 54:51.489
Of women.

54:51.491 --> 54:53.526
Hmm.

54:53.528 --> 54:55.462
I get that.

54:57.632 --> 54:59.499
Does that bother you?

55:00.902 --> 55:03.436
No, it doesn't bother me
in the least.

55:06.439 --> 55:08.375
Is that why you got beat up?

55:10.812 --> 55:13.579
Well, I was wearing
running shoes that night.

55:13.581 --> 55:16.949
But I guess I said something
about essence.

55:16.951 --> 55:19.417
That's awful.

55:19.419 --> 55:21.386
I'm so sorry.

55:21.388 --> 55:24.957
I'd been drinking.
I drank a lot in those days.

55:24.959 --> 55:28.761
Maybe if I hadn't been drunk,
I would've kept my mouth shut.

55:28.763 --> 55:30.529
Don't say that.

55:30.531 --> 55:32.731
There's no excuse
for what they did to you.

55:32.733 --> 55:35.835
It's a hate crime,
plain and simple.

55:35.837 --> 55:37.736
No matter what you said.

55:37.738 --> 55:39.674
