of my personal life.

56:16.043 --> 56:20.012
Everything from
before the attack is gone.

56:20.014 --> 56:23.115
All I remember about the attack

56:23.117 --> 56:26.451
was the word "queer."

56:26.453 --> 56:28.988
They called me queer.

56:28.990 --> 56:31.190
And...

56:31.192 --> 56:34.093
Tammy Wynette was playing
on the jukebox.

56:34.095 --> 56:36.463
"Stand by Your Man."

56:38.199 --> 56:40.933
That's all I remember.

56:40.935 --> 56:42.868
That's awful.

56:42.870 --> 56:45.671
You're lucky
they didn't kill you.

56:45.673 --> 56:46.972
I guess.

56:46.974 --> 56:49.975
I was lying in the road
for over an hour,

56:49.977 --> 56:51.844
and that's when Wendy found me.

56:51.846 --> 56:53.679
She was bartending that night.

56:53.681 --> 56:55.616
(PHONE RINGING)

56:57.251 --> 57:00.119
Um, just one second, okay?

57:00.121 --> 57:01.689
Oh, yeah.

57:07.929 --> 57:09.828
- Hello?
- Okay.

57:09.830 --> 57:11.530
Yes.

