contacted the family?

57:30.284 --> 57:32.284
All right, good.

57:32.286 --> 57:34.121
Okay, I'll be there.

57:35.957 --> 57:37.790
Okay, great.

57:37.792 --> 57:39.727
Thanks.

57:42.596 --> 57:44.163
