What are you gonna do?

57:51.205 --> 57:53.207
Do you like teapots?

57:54.575 --> 57:56.875
Yeah, I love tea.

57:56.877 --> 58:00.279
I love everything
to do with tea.

58:00.281 --> 58:01.847
I love making it.

58:01.849 --> 58:04.917
I love the ritual
of serving it.

58:04.919 --> 58:08.821
