building a teahouse,

58:08.823 --> 58:10.823
- now that I have a yard.
- Mm.

58:10.825 --> 58:13.826
Just a little one
in the backyard.

58:13.828 --> 58:16.996
The last time I had tea,
I was in the hospital.

58:16.998 --> 58:19.698
I bet. It has amazing
therapeutic benefits.

58:19.700 --> 58:21.100
Are you a nurse?

58:21.102 --> 58:23.936
I'm a vet tech.

58:23.938 --> 58:26.205
- A veterinarian technician.
- Oh.

58:26.207 --> 58:30.011
And I also volunteer
at Under One Woof.

58:31.145 --> 58:33.278
Under One Woof.

58:33.280 --> 58:35.781
- Get it? "Woof"?
- Mm...

58:35.783 --> 58:37.184
Animal shelter.

58:38.285 --> 58:40.586
- Mm.
- (NICOL LAUGHS)

58:40.588 --> 58:42.621
- Right.
- Okay.

58:42.623 --> 58:44.123
