59:34.875 --> 59:37.076
- What's with all the Nazi toys and shit, huh?
- Stop it.

59:37.078 --> 59:38.677
You some kind
of white supremacist

59:38.679 --> 59:41.080
- pedophile, Mark, huh?
- Stop it. Such a jerk.

59:41.082 --> 59:43.816
- Oh, I'm a jerk? I'm a jerk?
- (DOOR CLOSES, LOCK CLICKS)

59:43.818 --> 59:45.753
♪

59:51.659 --> 59:53.260
(GASPS)

59:54.929 --> 59:57.698
(GROANING)

01:00:04.405 --> 01:00:07.706
