want them, just toss 'em.

01:09:40.982 --> 01:09:42.948
Oh, no, no, no.
Are you kidding?

01:09:42.950 --> 01:09:45.886
I will add them
to the collection.

01:09:50.390 --> 01:09:54.426
Wow. So, this is what
200 pairs of shoes looks like.

01:09:54.428 --> 01:09:56.996
- 287.
- Wow.

01:09:56.998 --> 01:09:59.699
